To convert folder into other groups of HTMLs
	 * Generate a group HTML elements based on index.xml
	 * Insert these HTML elements into `${html}` in index.html file in the folder
	 * If there is an zdoc.css file, insert the zdoc.css into every generated HTML files
	 * If there are other css and js files, to copy all of other css and js files into the generated folders
	
To merge files into one
	 * The process is the same between PDF and HTML.
	 * It will generate chapters and the structure based on the index.xml
	 * Each zDoc files will be the content of chapters.